            . As I was going through St. Paul's Church Yard, on the 4th of November, in my way home, I met the prisoner and two more; I saw they were at a gentleman's pocket; I turned back and followed them; the gentleman went to an inn in <placeName id="t17721209-77-crimeloc384">Friday-street</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17721209-77-crimeloc384" type="placeName" value="Friday-street"></interp>
