                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17721209-77-off382 t17721209-77-crimeloc384"></join>; they stopt when he went in, and when he came out again, the prisoner picked his handkerchief out of his pocket; I pursued him and secured him with the gentleman's handkerchief upon him. The owner of the handkerchief had taken a place in the coach for Bath, and was to set out the next morning.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence.</p>
               <p>I picked up the handkerchief.</p>
